# int64Values

**Instance Property**

An array of 64-bit integers in the sequence.

## Declaration

```swift
var int64Values: [NSNumber] { get }
```

## Discussion

Only use this property when the sequence’s [doc://com.apple.coreml/documentation/CoreML/MLSequence/type] is [doc://com.apple.coreml/documentation/CoreML/MLFeatureType/int64].

## Retrieving the Sequence’s Values

- **stringValues**: An array of strings in the sequence.
